      • couchDb

        public void couchDb(org.testng.ITestResult iTest)
        Log Selenium Log to couchDb This overload, gets everything it needs from the ITestResult, simplifing the parameters Should be called from an AfterMethod, passing the ITestResult from the main test method through reflection example: protected void afterMethod(Method method, ITestResult result, Object[] params) Normally the AfterMethod would use its own ITestResult, but in this case we want the logs from the Before and After methods to be included in the main test log
